{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build and manage your ice cream business. Organize and upgrade your kitchen and inventories. Find new recipes and flavors, buy new ice-cream carts. Discover each location\u2019s favorite flavors and make customers happy.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Organize your Kitchen</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It all begins here. Start small, manage and upgrade your inventory, keep it loose or meticulously tight. Experiment with ingredients and different equipment.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174390/extras/kitchen_gif_3.gif?t=1737053296\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Make And Sell Ice Creams</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy ingredients. Start blending them and let it chill!. Plan your next staging correctly for your carts.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174390/extras/cart-load.gif?t=1737053296\" /><br><br><strong>Build your brand</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn money and buy new spots. Start with a cart and expand into a fleet of ice-cream carts, each with a menu to satisfy different location\u2019s flavor expectations.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174390/extras/sales.gif?t=1737053296\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Find New Recipes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn new recipes and unlock special ones throughout your journey. Each flavor has a distinct category, each location has it\u2019s own flavor personality. Get to know the locals, understand their tastes, and create treats that bring smiles.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174390/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737053296","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174390/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737053296","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store